## Example

```py
from view import new_app, h1

app = new_app()

@app.get("/")
async def index():
    return h1("Hello, view.py!")

app.run()
```

## Installation

**Python 3.8+ is required.**

### Development 

```
$ pip install git+https://github.com/ZeroIntensity/view.py
```

### Linux/macOS

```
$ python3 -m pip install -U view.py
```

### Windows

```
> py -3 -m pip install -U view.py
```
